message.entry: Trailing input arguments must occur in name-value pairs.
Bin edges must be a vector of length greater than or equal to 2.
Bin limits must be a finite and sorted datetime vector with 2 elements.
Bin width must be a scalar duration or calendarDuration, and must be positive and finite.
Bin edges must be a datetime vector with at least two elements.
''BinEdges'' input cannot be followed by any of ''NumBins'',''BinWidth'', ''BinMethod'', or ''BinLimits''.
EDGES must be a datetime array.
X must be a datetime array.
Bin edges must be a sorted datetime vector that does not contain NaTs.
